---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.jsx";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="IT Support & Fractional CTO Brisbane | Aurora ICT Total Care"
  page="services"
  description="Aurora ICT Total Care provides tailored IT support, planning, digital transformation leadership and Fractional CTO guidance for growing businesses that want worry-free technology care without MSP lock-in."
>
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="page-main">
    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 md:py-20">
      <div class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10">
        <div class="text-sm font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-purple);">Aurora ICT Total Care</div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold text-white mt-2">Worry-free IT total care for growing businesses</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl" style="color: var(--muted);">Aurora ICT cares for your business technology across planning, leadership and service — giving you practical IT support, senior guidance and independent advice without MSP lock-in or one-size-fits-all packages.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">Planning. Leadership. Service. All cared for by one independent technology partner.</p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-base md:text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">From everyday support to 1 / 3 / 5 year roadmaps, digital transformation and Fractional CTO guidance, Aurora ICT helps keep your technology clear, controlled and aligned with business growth.</p>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a href="/technology-health-check" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110" style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">Book a Technology Health Check</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white">Discuss Total IT Care</a>
        </div>
        <a href="/it-strategy-roadmap" class="mt-5 inline-block underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Explore the 1 / 3 / 5 year IT roadmap</a>

        <div class="mt-8 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/20"><h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Planning</h2><p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">Roadmaps, priorities, budgets, risks and transformation planning.</p></article>
          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/20"><h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Leadership</h2><p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">Fractional CTO guidance, governance, vendor-independent advice and senior escalation.</p></article>
          <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5 border border-white/20"><h2 class="text-white font-extrabold text-xl">Service</h2><p class="mt-2" style="color: var(--muted);">Level 1, 2 and 3 support, vendor coordination and practical issue resolution.</p></article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24 space-y-10">
      <section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h2 class="text-white font-bold">Total IT care</h2><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Support, planning, leadership and transformation guidance in one coordinated model.</p></article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h2 class="text-white font-bold">Tailored to your business</h2><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Scope and pricing shaped around your systems, users, risks, goals and budget.</p></article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h2 class="text-white font-bold">Vendor-independent</h2><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Advice based on what suits your business, not supplier incentives or preferred stacks.</p></article>
        <article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h2 class="text-white font-bold">Not an MSP</h2><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">A flexible support and leadership model, not a fixed helpdesk package.</p></article>
      </section>

      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10"><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">Planning, leadership and service — connected</h2><p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Many businesses have IT support, software providers, consultants and internal decision-makers all working separately. Aurora ICT Total Care brings the key parts together: practical support, senior technology leadership, roadmap planning, vendor coordination and transformation support.</p></section>

      <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <article class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8"><h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white">Planning: know where your technology is going</h2><p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Aurora ICT helps you move from reactive IT decisions to a clear technology direction. The 1 / 3 / 5 year roadmap gives your business a practical view of what needs attention now, what should be improved next, and what should be planned for longer-term growth.</p><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5" style="color: var(--muted);"><li>1 / 3 / 5 year IT roadmap</li><li>Technology priorities</li><li>Budget guidance</li><li>Risk visibility</li><li>Project sequencing</li><li>System and vendor review</li><li>Growth-aligned technology planning</li></ul><a href="/it-strategy-roadmap" class="mt-4 inline-block font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Explore the 1 / 3 / 5 year IT roadmap →</a></article>
        <article class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8"><h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white">Leadership: senior technology guidance without a full-time CTO</h2><p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Aurora ICT gives business leaders access to senior technology guidance without the cost of hiring a full-time CTO. That means clearer decisions, better vendor management, stronger project oversight and practical advice that aligns technology with business goals.</p><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5" style="color: var(--muted);"><li>Fractional CTO services</li><li>Senior escalation</li><li>Governance</li><li>Vendor-independent advice</li><li>Project oversight</li><li>Technology decision support</li><li>Business case support</li><li>Cost control</li><li>Risk and security guidance</li></ul><a href="/it-consulting" class="mt-4 inline-block font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">See Fractional CTO support →</a></article>
        <article class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8"><h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white">Service: practical IT support from Level 1 to Level 3</h2><p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Total Care includes practical support for everyday issues and more complex technical escalation. Aurora ICT can coordinate with vendors, support users, guide technical decisions and help make sure problems are resolved with business impact in mind.</p><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5" style="color: var(--muted);"><li>Level 1 everyday support</li><li>Level 2 systems, application and configuration troubleshooting</li><li>Level 3 escalation, infrastructure, security, integrations and complex issues</li><li>Vendor coordination</li><li>Support process improvement</li><li>Escalation ownership</li></ul><a href="/services" class="mt-4 inline-block font-bold" style="color: var(--color-accent-green);">Explore advisory and support services →</a></article>
      </section>

      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10"><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">Why Aurora ICT is different from a traditional MSP</h2><p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Traditional MSPs can be useful for standardised IT support, but many growing businesses need more than a ticket queue, a fixed technology stack and a monthly service tier. Aurora ICT is not an MSP. It is an independent technology partner focused on support, planning, leadership and business outcomes.</p></section>

      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10 overflow-x-auto"><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">Common MSP frustrations — and what Aurora ICT offers instead</h2><table class="mt-6 w-full text-left border-collapse"><thead><tr class="border-b border-white/20"><th class="py-3 pr-4 text-white">Common MSP frustration</th><th class="py-3 pl-4 text-white">Aurora ICT Total Care</th></tr></thead><tbody style="color: var(--muted);">
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Fixed service tiers that may not match the business</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Tailored scope and pricing based on actual needs</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Preferred vendor stacks or reseller arrangements</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Vendor-independent advice and recommendations</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Reactive ticket handling</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Support combined with planning and senior guidance</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Limited strategic input</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Fractional CTO-level leadership and decision support</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Tool or licence recommendations that may favour the provider</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Business-first technology decisions</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Escalations disappearing into a queue</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Senior oversight and practical ownership</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Unclear inclusions, exclusions or responsibilities</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Clear priorities, scope and accountability</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Focus on systems rather than business outcomes</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Technology aligned to growth, risk, efficiency and cost control</td></tr>
<tr class="border-b border-white/10"><td class="py-3 pr-4">Lock-in to one provider’s way of working</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Flexible model that can work with existing providers or replace fragmented arrangements</td></tr>
<tr><td class="py-3 pr-4">Standard packages proposed before understanding the business</td><td class="py-3 pl-4">Discovery first, then a tailored support and leadership model</td></tr>
</tbody></table></section>

      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10"><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">Built around your business, not a standard package</h2><p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Aurora ICT Total Care is shaped around how your business actually works. Before recommending the right package, Aurora ICT looks at your users, systems, vendors, risks, internal capability, growth plans and budget expectations.</p><div class="mt-6 grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-3" style="color: var(--muted);"><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Number of users and locations</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Current systems and applications</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Existing vendors and contracts</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Support needs and pain points</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Security and operational risks</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Internal capability</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Growth plans</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Digital transformation priorities</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-4">Budget expectations</div></div><p class="mt-5 font-semibold text-white">The result is a practical package that fits the business — not a one-size-fits-all MSP tier.</p></section>

      <section><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">What can be included in Aurora ICT Total Care</h2><div class="mt-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4"><article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h3 class="font-extrabold text-white">Level 1 support</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Everyday user, access, device and productivity support.</p></article><article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h3 class="font-extrabold text-white">Level 2 support</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Systems, applications, workflow, configuration and vendor troubleshooting.</p></article><article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h3 class="font-extrabold text-white">Level 3 support</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Complex escalation, infrastructure, security, integrations and architecture guidance.</p></article><article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h3 class="font-extrabold text-white">1 / 3 / 5 year roadmap</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Short, medium and long-term technology planning aligned to business growth.</p></article><article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h3 class="font-extrabold text-white">Digital transformation support</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">System selection, workflow improvement, automation, adoption and change support.</p></article><article class="glass rounded-2xl p-5"><h3 class="font-extrabold text-white">Fractional CTO services</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--muted);">Senior IT leadership, governance, vendor management, budget guidance, project oversight and risk reduction.</p></article></div></section>

      <section class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6"><article class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8"><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">Designed for growing businesses that need more than basic IT support</h2><ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5" style="color: var(--muted);"><li>Businesses without a full-time CTO or CIO</li><li>Owner-led businesses that need clearer technology direction</li><li>Directors, GMs and operations managers responsible for IT decisions</li><li>Businesses frustrated with reactive support</li><li>Businesses with too many systems, vendors or disconnected tools</li><li>Businesses preparing for growth, change, system upgrades or digital transformation</li><li>Businesses wanting better cost control and clearer priorities</li></ul></article>
      <article class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8"><h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white">The outcome: clearer, calmer, better-managed IT</h2><div class="mt-4 grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3" style="color: var(--muted);"><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Clearer IT ownership</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Less vendor noise</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Better escalation</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Faster practical decisions</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Reduced unnecessary spend</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Better cyber and operational risk visibility</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">More confident technology planning</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Stronger project oversight</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">A practical 1 / 3 / 5 year roadmap</div><div class="glass rounded-xl p-3">Technology that supports business growth instead of slowing it down</div></div></article></section>

      <section class="glass rounded-3xl glow p-8 md:p-10 text-center"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">Ready for IT support that thinks beyond the next ticket?</h2><p class="mt-3 text-lg" style="color: var(--muted);">Start with a practical review of your current systems, vendors, risks and priorities. From there, Aurora ICT can shape the right Total Care package for your business.</p><p class="mt-3" style="color: var(--muted);">Related services: <a href="/it-consulting" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">Fractional CTO guidance</a> and <a href="/it-strategy-roadmap" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white text-white">IT roadmap planning</a>.</p><div class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4"><a href="/technology-health-check" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-extrabold transition hover:brightness-110" style="background: var(--color-accent-green); color: #08110c; box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(57,255,122,0.22);">Book a Technology Health Check</a><a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold border border-white/15 bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/15 transition text-white">Contact Aurora ICT</a></div></section>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
